
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I go to Page 09 of Thoracic CT
Then 'Dynamic findings' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'COVID-19 CT Groups' checkbox
Then 'Suggestive for a COVID-19 pneumonia' radio button is enabled
And 'Imaging features are indeterminate, COVID-19 pneumonia possible' radio button is enabled
And 'Imaging features suggestiv for alternativ diagnosis' radio button is enabled
And 'CT-negative for pneumonic opacities' radio button is enabled
